# Movie Recommendation System

## Project Description
This project recommends Telugu movies based on similar genres using a content-based recommendation system.

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn

## Algorithm
- CountVectorizer
- Cosine Similarity

## Dataset
Custom Telugu movie dataset.

## Features
- User enters a movie name.
- System recommends similar Telugu movies.
- Fast and simple recommendation system.

## How to Run

Install libraries:

pip install pandas
pip install scikit-learn

Run:

python movie_recommendation.py
